		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津使用手上的<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀，进行至多4段的普通攻击，4段普攻均造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津用<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀划过，划出一道雷刃，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害，在近处会被</span><span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀打到也造成</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="435" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津召唤一个<span color="#e5d7fd">「</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#e5d7fd">祸津之雷眼</span><span color="#e5d7fd">」</span><span>，雷眼一段时间后爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">116.6%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，破坏</span><span color="#e5d7fd">「祸津之雷眼」</span><span>后祸津</span><span color="#ff9672">眩晕</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">在祸津技能间歇期时攻击，产生雷盾，抵挡伤害；受击超4次时，每次攻击会增加10%反击概率；反击时，迅速斩两刀分别造成<span color="#ffacff">16.6%,33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="437" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津将<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀指向空中，将武器变为</span><span color="#ff9999">梦想一心</span><span>，同时在其前方产生一道落雷，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，之后场景间歇出现落雷，一次施放3道，每道落雷造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="422" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津旋转<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀冲向玩家，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，并斩3刀，前两刀依次造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%,<br/>16.6%</span><span>伤害，较大的第三刀，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="437" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">眩晕时受击超8次时，将有48%的概率立即恢复，且每次受击都会增加6%恢复概率。祸津恢复<span color="#ffebbf">眩晕</span><span>后，在身边产生雷震击飞玩家，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害但不显示数字</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="437" height="201" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津斜拿<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀，震开附近玩家，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，召唤</span><span color="#e5d7fd">「</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#e5d7fd">祸津三重眼</span><span color="#e5d7fd">」</span><span>在场地上，雷眼一段时间后同时爆炸；<br/>被雷眼命中的个数不同，造成的伤害不一样，一个造成</span><span color="#ffacff">133.3%</span><span>伤害，两个造成2段</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害，三个造成3段</span><span color="#ffacff">13.3%</span><span>伤害，以上伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">闪避帧均无效</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津旋转<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀，产生大范围的落雷，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">66.6%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于祸津身后时，祸津转身划<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">薙</span><span>刀，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，随后产生爆破，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
