		<RichText x="66" y="1196" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="305" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津之雷眼：9次次数盾，击破可眩晕祸津。<br/>祸津三重眼：7次次数盾，击破可躲避爆炸。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<Group d:userLabel="Group_2">
			<RichText x="77" y="1147" fontFamily="汉仪润圆-65W" fontSize="25" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ff9999" width="38" height="29" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
				<content>
					<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="汉仪润圆-65W" fontSize="25" color="#ff9999">-50</p>
